data.title: Question #706313 “When will there be a new version coming out ??...” : Questions : BleachBit
data.meta_description:
Seems like the project is dead.
Have not seen an update in a long time.

When will there be one ?
Or, did Bleachbit cease to exist ?

If it stopped then I would like to know :  are there any alternatives to it ?
